{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"The idea behind the Stuxnet computer worm"},{"time":3000,"text":"is actually quite simple."},{"time":5000,"text":"We don't want Iran to get the bomb."},{"time":8000,"text":"Their major asset for developing nuclear weapons"},{"time":11000,"text":"is the Natanz uranium enrichment facility."},{"time":15000,"text":"The gray boxes that you see,"},{"time":17000,"text":"these are real-time control systems."},{"time":20000,"text":"Now if we manage to compromise these systems"},{"time":23000,"text":"that control drive speeds and valves,"},{"time":26000,"text":"we can actually cause a lot of problems"},{"time":29000,"text":"with the centrifuge."},{"time":31000,"text":"The gray boxes don't run Windows software;"},{"time":33000,"text":"they are a completely different technology."},{"time":36000,"text":"But if we manage"},{"time":38000,"text":"to place a good Windows virus"},{"time":41000,"text":"on a notebook"},{"time":43000,"text":"that is used by a maintenance engineer"},{"time":45000,"text":"to configure this gray box,"},{"time":48000,"text":"then we are in business."},{"time":50000,"text":"And this is the plot behind Stuxnet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":53000,"text":"So we start with a Windows dropper."},{"time":58000,"text":"The payload goes onto the gray box,"},{"time":61000,"text":"damages the centrifuge,"},{"time":63000,"text":"and the Iranian nuclear program is delayed --"},{"time":65000,"text":"mission accomplished."},{"time":67000,"text":"That's easy, huh?"},{"time":69000,"text":"I want to tell you how we found that out."},{"time":72000,"text":"When we started our research on Stuxnet six months ago,"},{"time":75000,"text":"it was completely unknown what the purpose of this thing was."},{"time":78000,"text":"The only thing that was known"},{"time":80000,"text":"is it's very, very complex on the Windows part, the dropper part,"},{"time":83000,"text":"used multiple zero-day vulnerabilities."},{"time":86000,"text":"And it seemed to want to do something"},{"time":89000,"text":"with these gray boxes, these real-time control systems."},{"time":91000,"text":"So that got our attention,"},{"time":93000,"text":"and we started a lab project"},{"time":95000,"text":"where we infected our environment with Stuxnet"},{"time":99000,"text":"and checked this thing out."},{"time":101000,"text":"And then some very funny things happened."},{"time":104000,"text":"Stuxnet behaved like a lab rat"},{"time":107000,"text":"that didn't like our cheese --"},{"time":110000,"text":"sniffed, but didn't want to eat."},{"time":112000,"text":"Didn't make sense to me."},{"time":114000,"text":"And after we experimented with different flavors of cheese,"},{"time":117000,"text":"I realized, well, this is a directed attack."},{"time":121000,"text":"It's completely directed."},{"time":123000,"text":"The dropper is prowling actively"},{"time":125000,"text":"on the gray box"},{"time":127000,"text":"if a specific configuration is found,"},{"time":130000,"text":"and even if the actual program code that it's trying to infect"},{"time":134000,"text":"is actually running on that target."},{"time":136000,"text":"And if not, Stuxnet does nothing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139000,"text":"So that really got my attention,"},{"time":141000,"text":"and we started to work on this"},{"time":143000,"text":"nearly around the clock,"},{"time":145000,"text":"because I thought, \"Well, we don't know what the target is."},{"time":148000,"text":"It could be, let's say for example,"},{"time":150000,"text":"a U.S. power plant,"},{"time":152000,"text":"or a chemical plant in Germany."},{"time":154000,"text":"So we better find out what the target is soon.\""},{"time":157000,"text":"So we extracted and decompiled"},{"time":159000,"text":"the attack code,"},{"time":161000,"text":"and we discovered that it's structured in two digital bombs --"},{"time":164000,"text":"a smaller one and a bigger one."},{"time":167000,"text":"And we also saw that they are very professionally engineered"},{"time":171000,"text":"by people who obviously had all insider information."},{"time":175000,"text":"They knew all the bits and bites"},{"time":177000,"text":"that they had to attack."},{"time":179000,"text":"They probably even know the shoe size of the operator."},{"time":182000,"text":"So they know everything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":184000,"text":"And if you have heard that the dropper of Stuxnet"},{"time":187000,"text":"is complex and high-tech,"},{"time":189000,"text":"let me tell you this:"},{"time":191000,"text":"the payload is rocket science."},{"time":193000,"text":"It's way above everything"},{"time":195000,"text":"that we have ever seen before."},{"time":198000,"text":"Here you see a sample of this actual attack code."},{"time":201000,"text":"We are talking about --"},{"time":203000,"text":"around about 15,000 lines of code."},{"time":206000,"text":"Looks pretty much like old-style assembly language."},{"time":209000,"text":"And I want to tell you how we were able"},{"time":211000,"text":"to make sense out of this code."},{"time":213000,"text":"So what we were looking for is, first of all, system function calls,"},{"time":216000,"text":"because we know what they do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218000,"text":"And then we were looking for timers and data structures"},{"time":222000,"text":"and trying to relate them to the real world --"},{"time":224000,"text":"to potential real world targets."},{"time":226000,"text":"So we do need target theories"},{"time":229000,"text":"that we can prove or disprove."},{"time":232000,"text":"In order to get target theories,"},{"time":234000,"text":"we remember"},{"time":236000,"text":"that it's definitely hardcore sabotage,"},{"time":238000,"text":"it must be a high-value target"},{"time":240000,"text":"and it is most likely located in Iran,"},{"time":243000,"text":"because that's where most of the infections had been reported."},{"time":247000,"text":"Now you don't find several thousand targets in that area."},{"time":250000,"text":"It basically boils down"},{"time":252000,"text":"to the Bushehr nuclear power plant"},{"time":254000,"text":"and to the Natanz fuel enrichment plant."}]},{"cues":[{"time":256000,"text":"So I told my assistant,"},{"time":258000,"text":"\"Get me a list of all centrifuge and power plant experts from our client base.\""},{"time":261000,"text":"And I phoned them up and picked their brain"},{"time":263000,"text":"in an effort to match their expertise"},{"time":265000,"text":"with what we found in code and data."},{"time":268000,"text":"And that worked pretty well."},{"time":270000,"text":"So we were able to associate"},{"time":272000,"text":"the small digital warhead"},{"time":274000,"text":"with the rotor control."},{"time":276000,"text":"The rotor is that moving part within the centrifuge,"},{"time":279000,"text":"that black object that you see."},{"time":281000,"text":"And if you manipulate the speed of this rotor,"},{"time":284000,"text":"you are actually able to crack the rotor"},{"time":286000,"text":"and eventually even have the centrifuge explode."},{"time":290000,"text":"What we also saw"},{"time":292000,"text":"is that the goal of the attack"},{"time":294000,"text":"was really to do it slowly and creepy --"},{"time":297000,"text":"obviously in an effort"},{"time":299000,"text":"to drive maintenance engineers crazy,"},{"time":302000,"text":"that they would not be able to figure this out quickly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":305000,"text":"The big digital warhead -- we had a shot at this"},{"time":308000,"text":"by looking very closely"},{"time":310000,"text":"at data and data structures."},{"time":312000,"text":"So for example, the number 164"},{"time":314000,"text":"really stands out in that code;"},{"time":316000,"text":"you can't overlook it."},{"time":318000,"text":"I started to research scientific literature"},{"time":320000,"text":"on how these centrifuges"},{"time":322000,"text":"are actually built in Natanz"},{"time":324000,"text":"and found they are structured"},{"time":326000,"text":"in what is called a cascade,"},{"time":328000,"text":"and each cascade holds 164 centrifuges."},{"time":332000,"text":"So that made sense, that was a match."}]},{"cues":[{"time":334000,"text":"And it even got better."},{"time":336000,"text":"These centrifuges in Iran"},{"time":338000,"text":"are subdivided into 15, what is called, stages."},{"time":342000,"text":"And guess what we found in the attack code?"},{"time":344000,"text":"An almost identical structure."},{"time":346000,"text":"So again, that was a real good match."},{"time":349000,"text":"And this gave us very high confidence for what we were looking at."},{"time":352000,"text":"Now don't get me wrong here, it didn't go like this."},{"time":355000,"text":"These results have been obtained"},{"time":358000,"text":"over several weeks of really hard labor."},{"time":361000,"text":"And we often went into just a dead end"},{"time":364000,"text":"and had to recover."}]},{"cues":[{"time":366000,"text":"Anyway, so we figured out"},{"time":368000,"text":"that both digital warheads"},{"time":370000,"text":"were actually aiming at one and the same target,"},{"time":372000,"text":"but from different angles."},{"time":374000,"text":"The small warhead is taking one cascade,"},{"time":377000,"text":"and spinning up the rotors and slowing them down,"},{"time":380000,"text":"and the big warhead"},{"time":382000,"text":"is talking to six cascades"},{"time":384000,"text":"and manipulating valves."},{"time":386000,"text":"So in all, we are very confident"},{"time":388000,"text":"that we have actually determined what the target is."},{"time":390000,"text":"It is Natanz, and it is only Natanz."},{"time":393000,"text":"So we don't have to worry"},{"time":395000,"text":"that other targets"},{"time":397000,"text":"might be hit by Stuxnet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":399000,"text":"Here's some very cool stuff that we saw --"},{"time":402000,"text":"really knocked my socks off."},{"time":404000,"text":"Down there is the gray box,"},{"time":406000,"text":"and on the top you see the centrifuges."},{"time":409000,"text":"Now what this thing does"},{"time":411000,"text":"is it intercepts the input values from sensors --"},{"time":414000,"text":"so for example, from pressure sensors"},{"time":416000,"text":"and vibration sensors --"},{"time":418000,"text":"and it provides legitimate program code,"},{"time":421000,"text":"which is still running during the attack,"},{"time":423000,"text":"with fake input data."},{"time":425000,"text":"And as a matter of fact, this fake input data"},{"time":427000,"text":"is actually prerecorded by Stuxnet."},{"time":430000,"text":"So it's just like from the Hollywood movies"},{"time":432000,"text":"where during the heist,"},{"time":434000,"text":"the observation camera is fed with prerecorded video."},{"time":437000,"text":"That's cool, huh?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":440000,"text":"The idea here is obviously"},{"time":442000,"text":"not only to fool the operators in the control room."},{"time":445000,"text":"It actually is much more dangerous and aggressive."},{"time":449000,"text":"The idea"},{"time":451000,"text":"is to circumvent a digital safety system."},{"time":455000,"text":"We need digital safety systems"},{"time":457000,"text":"where a human operator could not act quick enough."},{"time":460000,"text":"So for example, in a power plant,"},{"time":462000,"text":"when your big steam turbine gets too over speed,"},{"time":465000,"text":"you must open relief valves within a millisecond."},{"time":468000,"text":"Obviously, this cannot be done by a human operator."},{"time":471000,"text":"So this is where we need digital safety systems."},{"time":473000,"text":"And when they are compromised,"},{"time":475000,"text":"then real bad things can happen."},{"time":478000,"text":"Your plant can blow up."},{"time":480000,"text":"And neither your operators nor your safety system will notice it."},{"time":483000,"text":"That's scary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":485000,"text":"But it gets worse."},{"time":487000,"text":"And this is very important, what I'm going to say."},{"time":490000,"text":"Think about this:"},{"time":492000,"text":"this attack is generic."},{"time":495000,"text":"It doesn't have anything to do, in specifics,"},{"time":499000,"text":"with centrifuges,"},{"time":501000,"text":"with uranium enrichment."},{"time":504000,"text":"So it would work as well, for example,"},{"time":507000,"text":"in a power plant"},{"time":509000,"text":"or in an automobile factory."},{"time":512000,"text":"It is generic."},{"time":514000,"text":"And you don't have -- as an attacker --"},{"time":516000,"text":"you don't have to deliver this payload"},{"time":519000,"text":"by a USB stick,"},{"time":521000,"text":"as we saw it in the case of Stuxnet."},{"time":523000,"text":"You could also use conventional worm technology for spreading."},{"time":526000,"text":"Just spread it as wide as possible."},{"time":529000,"text":"And if you do that,"},{"time":531000,"text":"what you end up with"},{"time":533000,"text":"is a cyber weapon of mass destruction."},{"time":539000,"text":"That's the consequence"},{"time":541000,"text":"that we have to face."},{"time":544000,"text":"So unfortunately,"},{"time":547000,"text":"the biggest number of targets for such attacks"},{"time":550000,"text":"are not in the Middle East."},{"time":552000,"text":"They're in the United States and Europe and in Japan."},{"time":555000,"text":"So all of the green areas,"},{"time":557000,"text":"these are your target-rich environments."},{"time":560000,"text":"We have to face the consequences,"},{"time":563000,"text":"and we better start to prepare right now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":566000,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":568000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":574000,"text":"Chris Anderson: I've got a question."},{"time":578000,"text":"Ralph, it's been quite widely reported"},{"time":580000,"text":"that people assume that Mossad"},{"time":582000,"text":"is the main entity behind this."},{"time":584000,"text":"Is that your opinion?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":587000,"text":"Ralph Langner: Okay, you really want to hear that?"},{"time":589000,"text":"Yeah. Okay."},{"time":591000,"text":"My opinion is that the Mossad is involved,"},{"time":594000,"text":"but that the leading force is not Israel."},{"time":597000,"text":"So the leading force behind that"},{"time":599000,"text":"is the cyber superpower."},{"time":602000,"text":"There is only one,"},{"time":604000,"text":"and that's the United States --"},{"time":606000,"text":"fortunately, fortunately."},{"time":608000,"text":"Because otherwise,"},{"time":610000,"text":"our problems would even be bigger."}]},{"cues":[{"time":613000,"text":"CA: Thank you for scaring the living daylights out of us. Thank you, Ralph."}]},{"cues":[{"time":617000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}